name: RRVS_eICRProcessingStatusReason_eCR
title: eICR Processing Status Reason (eCR)
description: This value set contains codes that describe the reason for the processing status (warning or error).

concept.display: eICR was not processed with an error of: fatal problem with the eICR that was received
eICR was not processed with an error of: an ongoing server problem
eICR was not processed with an error of: significant content or format issues
eICR was processed with the severe warning of: invalid eICR identifier
eICR was processed with the severe warning of: required data not found
eICR was processed with the warning of: content or format issues
